            <div class="tw-typo-op-base [&_strong]:tw-text-op-default [&_strong]:tw-font-normal"><p>We accept Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover, ApplePay, Affirm, Klarna and PayPal. All online payments on oliverpeoples.com are completely secure, thanks to the Secure Socket Layer (SSL) encryption that is used for every transaction in order to ensure that your order is secure.</p></div>
