          <div>
            <p class="tw-typo-op-h4 tw-mb-op-spacings-md">Shipping & Returns</p>
            <div class="tw-typo-op-base [&_strong]:tw-text-op-default [&_strong]:tw-font-normal"><p>We offer free shipping on all orders within your country. Orders are usually delivered in 5 business days and are fully insured against loss, theft or damage.</p><p>Free Returns Return any product purchased on oliverpeoples.com for any reason within 45 days of receiving the shipment, and enjoy free returns from anywhere in the world.</p></div>
